org.drombler.acp.core.action

Interface MenuItemSupplierFactory<MenuItem,F extends MenuItemSupplierFactory<MenuItem,F>>

  • Type Parameters:
    MenuItem - the GUI toolkit specific type for menu items
    F - the type of the implementation class
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IdentityMenuItemSupplierFactory, PositionableMenuItemAdapterFactory

    public interface MenuItemSupplierFactory<MenuItem,F extends MenuItemSupplierFactory<MenuItem,F>>
    A menu item supplier factory creates MenuItemSuppliers for the according menu item.Implementations can associate some custom data with this factory which is needed by a custom MenuItemSortingStrategy and can pass them to the MenuItemSupplier.
    Author:
    puce
    See Also:
    MenuItemSortingStrategy
